{
  "texts": [
    "Kim et al. (2024) suggests that as AI visualization models like DALL-E continue to develop, so to must guidelines, regulations, and policies to address novel capabilities and ethical considerations.",
    "Concluding that AI-generated images should be utilized in an ethical manner that augments accuracy and integrity, which are foundational components of scientific communications (Kim et al. 2024).",
    "Another underpinning issue here is that it is not always clear when AI-generated text is involved, especially because AI text detectors at present are unreliable (Stokel-Walker 2024).",
    "This is supported by a recent study which similarly highlighted the challenges associated with the identification and detection of AI-generated content (Perkins et al. 2024).",
    "Several salient questions emerge from this discussion moving forward."
  ]
}